msgstr "按计划重启 Mihomo，例如每周一次或每天一次。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/service.js:217
msgid "Restart schedule:"
msgstr "重启计划:"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/service.js:223
